title: Hilarious Dentist Makes Parody Song About Clean Teeth to Ed Sheeran's 'Shape Of You'
text:
Hilarious Dentist Makes Parody Song About Clean Teeth to Ed Sheeran's 'Shape Of You' posted by Elvis Duran and the Morning Show “Boy, you know you need to brush, twice a day then get that floss in between. Come on now, follow my lead. Just go and give them a good clean.”  
Dr. Milad Shadrooho , a dentist from the UK, is making headlines with his parody song about clean teeth to the tune of Ed Sheeran 's new single, 'Shape Of You.' The doctor has made a name for himself with a collection of parody songs about teeth. He even has a whole website dedicated to his craft at singingdentist.co.uk ! 
His latest installment is all about getting your teeth really, really clean! A post shared by Singing Dentist (@dentistsinging) on Feb 20, 2017 at 8:44am PST
